---
title: Mac ’n’ Cheese Bar with Bacon One recipe—endless ways to enjoy!
description: How do you please everyone at dinner? A mac ’n’ cheese bar! You’ll set out luscious baked mac ’n’ cheese with toppings galore: toasted everything-bagel breadcrumbs, roasted broccoli, juicy diced tomato, and tangy pickled jalapeños, then let everyone create their own perfect plate! Order bacon to add smoky crispness!
